      │                                         │
      ▼                                         ▼
Load events.json                         Fetch from Room DB
      │                                         │
      ▼                                         │
Insert into Room DB                           Emit Flow
      │                                         │
      └───────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                      ▼
               Room emits data (Flow)
                      │
                      ▼
               ViewModel receives list
                      │
                      ▼
             UI observes & updates RecyclerView

